Package org.jcvi.jillion.shared.fasta

Common classes that are used the different types of Fasta (nucleotide fasta, protein fasta etc) but aren't meant to be used by Jillion users.

See: Description

    Class Description
    AbstractFastaFileDataStoreBuilder<T,S extends Sequence<T>,F extends FastaRecord<T,S>,SD extends DataStore<S>,D extends FastaDataStore<T,S,F,SD>>

    AbstractFastaRecordBuilder<T,S extends Sequence<T>,F extends FastaRecord<T,S>,B extends AbstractFastaRecordBuilder<T,S,F,B>>
    AbstractFastaRecordBuilder is an abstract class that handles all the boilerplate code for building a FastaRecord.

    AbstractResidueFastaWriter<R extends Residue,S extends ResidueSequence<R,S,B>,B extends ResidueSequenceBuilder<R,S>,F extends FastaRecord<R,S>>
    AbstractResidueFastaWriter is an abstract implementation of a FastaWriter that writes ResidueSequences.
    AbstractResidueFastaWriter.Builder<R extends Residue,S extends ResidueSequence<R,S,B>,B extends ResidueSequenceBuilder<R,S>,F extends FastaRecord<R,S>,W extends FastaWriter<R,S,F>,T extends AbstractResidueFastaWriter.Builder<R,S,B,F,W,T>>
    Builder creates a builder instance that will build a FastaWriter using the given OutputStream and any additional configuration given.
